        <div class="entry-summary">
            <p><img src='http://cfile25.uf.tistory.com/image/992BFB355A505D2915A066' style='max-width:250px;min-width:0px;' onError='this.style.display="none"' /></p>
<h1>3줄 요약 </h1>
<div style='color:#fff;background-color:#000;border-radius:10px;'>
<ol>
<li><span>고용 안정을 위해 ‘일자리 안정자금’ 지원</span></li>
<li><span>지난 2016년 8월, 음주운전 단속에 적발된 차량을 경찰서로 몰고 오던 <small>&#8230;중략&#8230;</small>  시 단속 미달 수치가 나올 경우에는 경찰서에서 견인 비용을 부담합니다.</span></li>
<li><span>올해부터는 신입사원과 육아휴직자의 연차휴가가 확대됩니다.신입사원의 경우, <small>&#8230;중략&#8230;</small> 출근한 것으로 간주해 연차휴가를 산정합니다.         병사봉급 인상</span></li>
</ol>
</div>
<p><span id="more-7348"></span></p>
<p><iframe src='http://ad.selfhow.com/rd' width='100%' border=0 frameborder=0 style='height:auto;width:100%'></iframe></p>
<hr />
<div class="tt_adsense_top" style="margin-bottom:30px">
<!-- 반응형자동 --></p>
</div>
<div style="text-align:center;margin:0 0 10px 0;">
<!-- 가로긴사각형 --></p>
</div>
<p class="0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 36pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">2018</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 36pt;">년 새해 달라지는 제도</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0">
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">최저시급 인상 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">(7530</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">원</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">)</span></b></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">2018</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">년 최저임금이 시간급 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">7,530</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">원으로 작년 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">6,470</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">원 보다 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">16.4% </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">인상됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월급으로 환산하면 주 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">40</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">시간을 기준으로</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">(</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">주당 유급 주휴 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">8</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">시간 포함</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">) 157</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">3,770</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">원입니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">최저임금은 사용</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">근로자뿐만 아니라 임시직 일용직 시간제근로자 외국인근로자 등 고용형태나 국적에 관계없이 모두 적용됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">안정적으로 고용된 상용근로자를 포함해 임시직</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일용직</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">시간제 근로자</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">외국인 근로자 등</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">고용 형태나 국적에 관계없이 모두 적용 된다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">또한 최저임금보다 적은 금액을 지급하는 사업장은 적발될 경우 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">2000</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원 이하의</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">과태료를 부과해야 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0" style="text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span class="imageblock" style="display:inline-block;width:820px;width: 820px; height: 936px;;height:auto;max-width:100%"><img filemime="image/jpeg" filename="최저시급.jpg" height="936" src="http://cfile25.uf.tistory.com/image/992BFB355A505D2915A066" style="width: 820px; height: 936px;" width="820"/></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"></span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><br /></span></b></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><br /></span></b></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><br /></span></b></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><br /></span></b></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><br /></span></b></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">고용 안정을 위해 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">‘</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">일자리 안정자금</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">’ </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">지원</span></b></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">시급이 올라 기쁜점도 있는 반면</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">최저임금이 오르게 되면서 상품의 판매가도 폭등할 것으로</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">예상이 되며</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">채용의 감소도 불러올 것입니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">경비원의 최저임금이 오르면서 관리비도 덩달아 오르니 이를 부담스러워 한 주민들과</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">아파트에서 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">‘</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">경비원 줄이기</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">’</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">를 확산시켜 경비원의 수를 감축시키려 하고 있습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">관리비 절감 효과를 위해 국가에서 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">‘</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일자리 안정자금</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">’</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">도 지원하고 있습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">원칙은 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">30</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">인 미만 고용 사업주에 고용자의 월급의 일부를 지원하나</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">아파트나 다세대 주택 등의 경비원</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">청소원에 대해서는 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">30</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">인 이상 사업주도 지원 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">이처럼 일자리 안정자금은 최저임금 인상에 따른 소상공인</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">영세 중소기업의 경영상의</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">어려움과 노동자의 고용안정도 완화해 줄 예정입니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">. </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">최저임금과 더불어 실업급여 지급 수준도 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">‘</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">실직 전 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">3</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">개월간 평균임금의 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">50%’</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">에서</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">‘60%’</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">로 상승하며</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, 90~240</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일간 나오던 실업급여는 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">120~270</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일간 받을 수 있게 됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"></span></p>
<p class="0" style="text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span class="imageblock" style="display:inline-block;width:820px;width: 820px; height: 389px;;height:auto;max-width:100%"><img filemime="image/jpeg" filename="경비원.jpg" height="389" src="http://cfile28.uf.tistory.com/image/99F783415A505E571EC60A" style="width: 820px; height: 389px;" width="820"/></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt;"><b><span style="color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><br /></span></b></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt;"><b><span style="color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">출퇴근 교통사고도 업무상 재해 인정</span></b></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">2018</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">년 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일부터 출퇴근 중 대중교통</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">자가용</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">자전거</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">도보 등 다양한 수단을 이용하다</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">사고가 발생할 경우</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">산업재해로 인정을 해준다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">기존에는 사업주가 제공하는 교통수단인 통근버스 등을 이용하던 중 발생한 사고만을 산재로 인정했었지만</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">그 범위가 확대된 것입니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">근로복지공단 지침에 따르면</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">출퇴근 재해는 업무에 종사하기 위해 또는 업무를 마치면서</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">이뤄지는 행위 중 이동경로 상에서 발생한 재해로 규정되며</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">이동경로는 교통수단을</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">이용하여 누구나 이용할 수 있다고 인정되는 통상경로입니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">통상적 출퇴근 경로에서 벗어나 일상생활에 필요한 행위를 하다 사고가 발생하더라도 업무상</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">재해로 간주하며</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">그 예로는 일용품 구매</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">선거권 행사</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">진료</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">가족 병간호</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">직무 관련 교육 등이 포함된다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">산업재해 신청 편의도 높아지며 종전엔 산재보험급여 청구를 위해 근로자가 직접 경찰서나</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">지구대를 방문하여 교통사고 사실확인원을 발급받아 공단에 제출해야 했지만</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">,</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">향후 경찰서와 공단이 교통사고 확인에 필요한 정보를 전산망으로 공유해 주어</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">굳이 경찰서에 방문하지 않아도 된다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">공단은 지원사업의 차질 없는 수행을 위해 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">‘</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일자리안정지원단</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">’</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">을 신설했으며</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">,</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">전국 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">56</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">개 소속 기관에 전담지원팀을 만들고</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">새로운 직업병에 대한 전문성 강화를 위해</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">‘</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">업무상질병부</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">’</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">를 신설했습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">보험급여 부정수급 조사 강화를 위해 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">‘</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">부정수급예방부</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">’</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">도 설치했다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"></span></p>
<p class="0" style="text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span class="imageblock" style="display:inline-block;width:820px;;height:auto;max-width:100%"><img filemime="image/jpeg" filename="출퇴근.jpg" height="552" src="http://cfile28.uf.tistory.com/image/99C07F3E5A505E890BCC43" style="" width="820"/></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><br /></span></b></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><br /></span></b></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><br /></span></b></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><br /></span></b></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><br /></span></b></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><br /></span></b></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><br /></span></b></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><br /></span></b></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">음주운전 단속 차량 견인</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">비용은 운전자가</span></b></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">지난 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">2016</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">년 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">8</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">음주운전 단속에 적발된 차량을 경찰서로 몰고 오던 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">26</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">살 순경이</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">교통사고로 사망하는 안타까운 사건이 있었습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">실제로 음주단속 경찰관은 단속 차량을 직접 운전해 경찰서로 이동하고</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">음주운전자를</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">집에 데려다 주기까지 하는 일을 하고 있었습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">경찰의 근무 환경 개선을 위해 음주 단속 차량은 무조건 견인 조치 될 예정입니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">오는 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">4</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">25</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일부터 경찰이 음주 운전자를 적발했을 때</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">운전자가 대체운전자 호출을</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">거부하거나 차량 운행을 허용하지 않는 경우 차량을 견인하며</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">비용은 추후 운전자가</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">부담하며 재측정 시 단속 미달 수치가 나올 경우에는 경찰서에서 견인 비용을 부담합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"></span></p>
<p class="0" style="text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span class="imageblock" style="display:inline-block;width:820px;width: 820px; height: 485px;;height:auto;max-width:100%"><img filemime="image/jpeg" filename="음주단속.jpg" height="485" src="http://cfile23.uf.tistory.com/image/99D8A4345A505EBE102DE9" style="width: 820px; height: 485px;" width="820"/></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">교통법규 상습 위반 시 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">‘</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">유치장</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">’</span></b></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">속도</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">신호위반 등 상습 교통법규 위반자 특별관리 제도를 본격 시행 한다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">대형사고 위험이 큰 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">36</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">인승 이상 대형 승합차와 대형 화물차에 대해 제도를 먼저 시행하며</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">4</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월부터는 사업용 자동차</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, 7</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월에는 전체 자동차까지 범위를 넓힌다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">특별관리 대상은 연간 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">10</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">회 이상 과태료를 부과 받은 차량 소유자로 대상에 지정되면</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">교통경찰 전산망에 등록이 됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">이 대상에서 해제되기 위해서는 과태료와 범칙금을 완납하고 이 후 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">년간 추가 위반이 없어야 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만약</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">특별관리 대상자가 과태료를 부과하지 않을 경우에는 범칙금과 벌점을 물려 처벌할 수 있도록 출석요구서를 발송한다고 하네요</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">대상 지정 이후에도 교통법규를 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">3</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">차례 이상 위반하면 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">30</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일 미만 유치장 구류처분까지 가능한</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">즉결 심판에 넘겨지며</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">경찰에 따르면 실제로 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">년간 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">10</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">회 이상 과태료를 부과받은 상습</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">교통법규 위반자는 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">년 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">회 과태료를 문 운전자보다 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">2</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">배 이상 인명사고 위험이 커 엄하게</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">법을 집행할 전망이라고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"></span></p>
<p class="0" style="text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span class="imageblock" style="display:inline-block;width:820px;width: 820px; height: 546px;;height:auto;max-width:100%"><img filemime="image/jpeg" filename="운전.jpg" height="546" src="http://cfile4.uf.tistory.com/image/9932974A5A505F760FC6E2" style="width: 820px; height: 546px;" width="820"/></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt;"><b><span style="color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">보복운전자도 의무 교육 대상에 추가</span></b></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">지난 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">3</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">대전에서 승용차가 오토바이를 고의로 들이받는 사건이 있었습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">승용차 운전자릐 범행 이유는 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">‘</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">비켜주지 않아서</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">’</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">였습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">같은 달 깜빡이 없이 끼어든 택시를 쫓아가 택기 기사를 폭행한 사건도 있었습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">오는 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">4</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">25</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일부터 보복운전으로 면허 취소나 정지처분을 받을 시</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">특별교통안전교육을</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">받아야 한다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">이 특별교통안전교육은 교통법규 준수와 안전을 위한 교육으로 도로교통공단에서 실시합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">사면을 받더라도 교육은 의무적으로 수료해야 하며</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">교육비는 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">시간 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">5000</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">원이었으나</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1000</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">원 인상한 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">6000</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">원으로 변경됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"></span></p>
<p class="0" style="text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span class="imageblock" style="display:inline-block;width:820px;width: 820px; height: 431px;;height:auto;max-width:100%"><img filemime="image/jpeg" filename="보복운전.png" height="431" src="http://cfile28.uf.tistory.com/image/99C5A44A5A505FAC1EA561" style="width: 820px; height: 431px;" width="820"/></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">도로 외 공간</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">다른 차 긁으면 연락처를 남겨야한다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">.</span></b></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">개정된 도로교통법 도로 외 공간에서 운전 중 남의 차를 긁는 등 파손을 했다면</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">연락처를 남겨야 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">파손하는 사고를 낸 후 연락처를 남기지 않는다면 범칙금이 부과됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">도로 외 공간의 대표적인 예는 학교</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">공공기관</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">병원</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">아파트 단지</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">백화점 등의</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">옥외</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">옥내 주차장과 차량 이동로입니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">시설자체에서 차량의 주정차 공간</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">이동로를 확보라고 관리하는 모든 곳에 해당이 됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">앞으로는 탑승자 없이 세워진 차량을 파손하고 자리를 뜨게되면 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">20</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원 이하의 벌금을 </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">내야하며 이 제도는 이미 지난 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">10</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월부터 시행되고 있다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"></span></p>
<p class="0" style="text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span class="imageblock" style="display:inline-block;width:820px;width: 820px; height: 479px;;height:auto;max-width:100%"><img filemime="image/jpeg" filename="주차.jpg" height="479" src="http://cfile24.uf.tistory.com/image/9969733C5A505FF9147B29" style="width: 820px; height: 479px;" width="820"/></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">공중화장실 휴지통 사라진다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">.</span></b></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">우리나라에 오는 외국인이 가장 놀라는 문화 중 하나가 바로 화장실 안에 비치된 휴지통이라고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">미관을 해치고 악취를 유발하는 원인인 휴지통이 굳이 왜 있는지 이해를 못한다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">외국의 경우에는 화장실 내에 휴지통이 따로 없으나</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">우리나라에만 유독 휴지통이 꼭 비치되어 있으며 이는 과거 우리나라가 신문지</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">질 낮은 휴지를 사용하여 변기가 자주 막혔기 때문이라고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">하지만 최근에는 물에 잘 풀리는 화장지들이 대부분이기 때문에 휴지통의 필요성이 없어지게 되었습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">지난해 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">5</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">‘</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">공중화장실 들에 관한 법률 시행령</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">’ </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일부 개정안이 국무회의를 통화했으며</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">,</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">이후 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">9</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일부터는 지하철 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1~8</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">호전 모든 역에서 휴지통이 사라졌으며</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, 1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일부터 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">9</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">호선을</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">포함한 모든 공중화장실 휴지통이 사라진다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">사용한 휴지는 변기에 버리고 여성 위생용품은 따로 설치되어 있는 수거함에 버리면 된다고 하네요</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"></span></p>
<p class="0" style="text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span class="imageblock" style="display:inline-block;width:820px;width: 820px; height: 461px;;height:auto;max-width:100%"><img filemime="image/jpeg" filename="화장실.jpg" height="461" src="http://cfile24.uf.tistory.com/image/99D7813B5A50603914A907" style="width: 820px; height: 461px;" width="820"/></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">소방차 길 터주지 않는 운전자</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">과태료 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">200</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">만원</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">!</span></b></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">화재 진압을 위한 소방차 출동의 골든타임은 단 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">5</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">분이라고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">화재 발생 후 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">5</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">분이 지나면 연소 확산속도와 피해가 급격하게 증가하여 진화에 어려움이</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">생기지만</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">골든타임 내에 사고현장에 도착하기 위해 사이렌을 울리며 접근하는 소방차에게</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">길을 터주지 않는 운전자도 꽤 많다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">이에 지난 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">12</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">26</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일부터 현행 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">20</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원이었던 과태료를 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">10</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">배 상향 조정하여 소방차의</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">진로 양보 의무를 어기는 운전자는 과태료 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">200</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원이 부과된다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">소방차를 포함한 구급차 등 긴급차량이 후방에서 접근할 경우</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">운전자는 도로 좌우로 움직여</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">길을 터줘야 한다고 하네요</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"></span></p>
<p class="0" style="text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span class="imageblock" style="display:inline-block;width:820px;width: 820px; height: 546px;;height:auto;max-width:100%"><img filemime="image/jpeg" filename="소방차.jpg" height="546" src="http://cfile23.uf.tistory.com/image/99C5413D5A50607F14723B" style="width: 820px; height: 546px;" width="820"/></span></p>
<p class="0" style="text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; color: rgb(0, 85, 255); font-size: 14pt;">가족관계 증명서</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; color: rgb(0, 85, 255); font-size: 14pt;">, 24</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; color: rgb(0, 85, 255); font-size: 14pt;">시간 발급 가능</span></b></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">가족관계증명서는 가까운 동사무소나 무인발급기에서 그리고 인터넷에서 발급할 수 있습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">하지만 이용할 수 있는 시간이 정해져 있어 불편함을 호소하는 이들이 많았습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">인터넷의 경우에도 평일 밤 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">10</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">시부터 다음날 오전 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">8</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">시까지는 서비스를 이용할 수 없었습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">오는 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">15</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일부터 인터넷으로 발급할 수 있는 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">‘</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">대법원 전자가족관계등록시스템</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">’</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">의</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">이용 제한 시간이 사라지면서 언제든지 필요한 시간에 가족관계증명서를 발급할 수 있게 되며</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">오는 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">5</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월부터는 이 시스템으로 출생신고도 가능해질 전망이라고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">출생신고는 가족관계등록관서를 직접 방문해야만 가능했지만</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일선 병원과 </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">건강보험심사평가원의 협조를 얻는다면 인터넷으로도 출생신고가 가능해진다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"></span></p>
<p class="0" style="text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span class="imageblock" style="display:inline-block;width:820px;width: 820px; height: 398px;;height:auto;max-width:100%"><img filemime="image/jpeg" filename="가족관계증명서.jpg" height="398" src="http://cfile22.uf.tistory.com/image/996AA83B5A5060BB263F06" style="width: 820px; height: 398px;" width="820"/></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt;"><b><span style="color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">성범죄 피해자 지원 확대</span></b></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">몰래카메라</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">보복성 영상물 등 디지털 성범죄 피해자들은 상반기부터 지원기관을 통해</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">종합적인 서비스를 지원 받을 수 있습니다</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">지원기관은 피해자들에게 유포 영상물 삭제</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">경찰 신고에 필요한 피해 사례 수집</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">,</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">사후 모니터링 등의 서비스를 제공하며 상담</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">무료법률서비스</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">의료비 등도 지원됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">디지털 성범죄 피해상담 창구인 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">‘</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">여성긴급전화 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1366’</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">도 운영하며</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">국회는 이를 위해</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">여성가족부에 예산 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">7</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">억</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">4000</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원을 배정했다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">성폭력</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">가정폭력을 당한 여성에게 지원되는 임대주택이 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">295</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">가구에서 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">315</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">가구로 늘어나며</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">피해 여성을 위한 쉼터도 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">2</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">곳 늘어난 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">28</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">곳이 됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">성매매 피해 아동</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">청소년을 위한 지원센터도 신규로 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">7</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">곳 지정되었다고 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"></span></p>
<p class="0" style="text-align: center; clear: none; float: none;"><span class="imageblock" style="display:inline-block;width:820px;width: 820px; height: 546px;;height:auto;max-width:100%"><img filemime="image/jpeg" filename="성범죄.jpg" height="546" src="http://cfile8.uf.tistory.com/image/995BC8365A50610D272127" style="width: 820px; height: 546px;" width="820"/></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><font face="Dotum, 돋움"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 187, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b><span style="font-size: 14pt;">그 외 달라지는 제도들</span></b></span></font></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><b><span style="font-size: 14pt;">연차휴가 확대</span></b></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">올해부터는 신입사원과 육아휴직자의 연차휴가가 확대됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">신입사원의 경우</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">입사 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">년차에 최대 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">11</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, 2</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">년차에 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">15</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일 등 총 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">26</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일의 연차유급휴가를 </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">보장받을 수 있습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">. </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">육아휴직자 또한 휴직기간을 출근한 것으로 간주해 연차휴가를 산정합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><b><span style="font-size: 14pt;">병사봉급 인상</span></b></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">올해부터 병장월급이 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">21</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">6,000</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">원에서 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">40</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">5,700</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">원으로 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">88% </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">인상됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">예비군 훈련 보상비도 하루 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원에서 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">5,000</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">원으로 오릅니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">교통비도 기존엔 이동거리와 상관없이 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">7,000</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">원을 받았지만</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">앞으론 이동거리가 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">30</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; letter-spacing: 0pt;">㎞</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">를 넘을 경우 추가지급합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">국토교통부 시외버스 운임단가</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">(</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; letter-spacing: 0pt;">㎞</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">당 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">116.14</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">원</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">) </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">기준</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">소득</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">·</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">법인세 최고세율 인상</span></b></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">올해부터는 종합소득과세표준 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">3</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">억원 초과 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">5</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">억원 이하 구간의 세율이 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">38%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">에서 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">40%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">로</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">,</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">5</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">억원 초과 구간의 세율이 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">40%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">에서 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">42%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">로 높아집니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">또 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일부터 개시하는 사업연도분부터 과세표준이 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">3,000</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">억원을 넘는 구간의</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">법인세율이 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">22%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">에서 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">25%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">로 인상됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><b><span style="font-size: 14pt;">전통시장 소득공제 확대</span></b></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">전통시장과 대중교통에 대한 신용카드 소득공제율이 기존 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">30%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">에서 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">40%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">로 높아집니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">또 총급여 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">7,000</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원 이하인 근로자의 도서</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">공연비 지출은 공제율 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">30%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">를 적용하되</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">,</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">내년 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">7</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월부터 한도가 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">100</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원 늘어납니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt;"><b><span style="color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">해외 카드 사용내역 제출대상 확대</span></b></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">기존엔 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">‘</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">물품구매액</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">+</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">인출금액</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">’</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">의 분기별 총액이 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">5,000</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">달러 이상이면 매 분기 다음달 말일에</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">사용내역이 관세청장에게 제출됐습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">하지만 올해 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">2</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월부터는 물품구매액 또는 인출금액이 건당 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">600</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">달러 이상이면 실시간으로 제출됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">즉</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">해외에서 면세한도 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">600</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">달러를 초과하는 물품을 결제하면 관세청에 바로 보고된다는 점</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">! </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">유의하셔야 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><b><span style="font-size: 14pt;">최고금리 인하</span></b></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">2</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">8</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일부터 법정 최고금리가 사인 간의 일반 거래의 경우 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">25%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">에서 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">24%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">로</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">대부업자 및 여신금융기관은 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">27.9%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">에서 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">24%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">로 각각 낮아집니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><b><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">ISA</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">제도 개선</span></b></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">총급여 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">5,000</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원 이하 근로자와 종합소득금액 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">3,500</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원 이하 사업자의 경우 </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">개인종합자산관리계좌</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">(ISA) </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만기 인출 시 비과세 한도가 이자소득액 기준으로</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">현행 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">250</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원에서 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">400</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원으로 확대됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">또 납입한 원금의 범위 내에서 중도 인출하더라도 세제 혜택 받은 부분을 추징하지 않습니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><b><span style="font-size: 14pt;">신혼부부 혜택 강화</span></b></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">신혼부부 주택구입 금리 인하</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월부터 생애 최초로 주택을 구입하는 부부 중 부부합산 연 소득이 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">7,000</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원 이하인</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">신혼부부에 기존 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">0.2% </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">우대금리에 더해 금리를 최대 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">0.35%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">포인트 추가 인하합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt;"><b><span style="color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">신혼부부 대출금리 우대</span></b></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">신혼부부 전용으로 전세대출을 받을시 대출비율을 기존 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">70%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">에서 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">80%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">로 확대합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">. </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">대출한도는 수도권 기준 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">억</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">7,000</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원으로 상향합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">. </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">금리도 최대 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">0.4%</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">포인트 추가 인하합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; color: rgb(0, 85, 255);"><b><span style="font-size: 14pt;">의료비 본인부담상한액 인하</span></b></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">소득분위 하위계층</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">(50% </span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">이하</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">)</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">의 연간 본인부담상한액이 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">80</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">~150</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">만원으로 낮아져 건강보험 혜택이 강화됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">본인부담상한제란</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">, 1</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">년간 지불한 건강보험 본인부담이 소득수준에 따른 개인별 상한금액을 넘을 경우 초과금을 국민건강보험공단이 부담하는 제도입니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움; font-size: 14pt;"><b><span style="color: rgb(0, 85, 255);">이혼 후 태어난 아이 생부 출생신고</span></b></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"><br /></span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[if !supportEmptyParas]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span><!--[endif]--><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;"> </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">올해 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">2</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">월부터 이혼 후 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">300</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일 이내에 태어난 자녀는 소송 없이 간단한 허가 청구를 통해</span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">전 남편이 아닌 생부를 아버지로 출생신고 할 수 있게 됩니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">. </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">현행법에 따르면 이혼 후 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">300</span><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">일 이내에 태어난 아이는 무조건 전 남편의 아이로 </span></p>
<p class="0"><span style="font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">가족관계등록부에 올려야 합니다</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0pt; font-family: Dotum, 돋움;">.</span></p>
<div style="text-align:center;margin:10px 0 10px 0;clear:both">
<div style="display:inline;text-align:center;">
<!-- 작은사각형 --></p>
</div>
<div style="display:inline;text-align:center;">
<!-- 작은사각형 --></p>
</div>
